description:
Emily Remler Guitar Lesson. Walking Bass Lines and Intro to Subdomiant Minors.  (See below)

For more information on Emily's life and music, visit http://www.allthingsemily.com

Index of this lesson:   http://www.allthingsemily.com/pdfimages/WalkingBasslineIndex.pdf
Sheet music:  http://www.allthingsemily.com/pdfimages/WalkingBasslineDocs.pdf

Thanks for stopping by and if you like what you hear, leave a comment.
title: Walking Bass and Subdominant Minors
